WIFI: For wifi, install `broadcom-wl-dkms`

SUBSCRIBE: Subscribe to arch-announce for any manual updates required

PACMAN_CACHE: Do not delete pacman-cache /var/cache/pacman/pkg

IGNORE_PACKAGE: update /etc/pacman.conf, edit IgnorePkg line to include packages that you don't want to update(linux kernel)

INSTALLING_PACKAGING: Never do pacman -Sy <package_name> instead of pacman -Syu <package_name>; run pacman -Syu before installing any package

DOWNGRADE: Not recommened, use timeshift for backup